tml\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ilc1719468669617.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ilc1719468669617.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"bav1665703126798\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      TextArea\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"bav1665703126798__textarea_386556\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The TextArea widget represents a text field in a static server page and can be used to display and enter data on multiple lines.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"bav1665703126798__topic_d114983e1_d114984e1_d114985e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bav1665703126798__p_d114986e1_d114987e1_d114988e1\">XHTML Specification: <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;x-subst type=\"textarea\"&gt;</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bav1665703126798__p_d114989e1_d114990e1_d114991e1\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fdp1719467376341.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fdp1719467376341.html\" title=\"XHTML placeholder for the USP widget and field data that will be generated in the HTML sent to the browser.\">&lt;x-subst type=\"WidgetType\"&gt;</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bav1665703126798__topic_d81617e1_d81618e1_d81619e1_d81620e1_d81621e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1139078e72\">\n                       \n Widget Properties\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"bav1665703126798__table_d14126e1_d14127e1_d14128e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Widget Properties</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bav1665703126798__table_d14126e1_d14127e1_d14128e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Property</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bav1665703126798__table_d14126e1_d14127e1_d14128e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description/More Information</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bav1665703126798__table_d14126e1_d14127e1_d14128e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pne1665703108090.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pne1665703108090.html\" title=\"In a static server page, exclude the field or entity if it does not need to be sent to the browser.\">Exclude</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bav1665703126798__table_d14126e1_d14127e1_d14128e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Exclude the field if it does not need to be sent to the browser.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bav1665703126798__table_d14126e1_d14127e1_d14128e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Rows</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bav1665703126798__table_d14126e1_d14127e1_d14128e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Height of the field.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bav1665703126798__table_d14126e1_d14127e1_d14128e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Columns</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bav1665703126798__table_d14126e1_d14127e1_d14128e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Width of the field.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bav1665703126798__topic_d81622e1_d81623e1_d81624e1_d81625e1_d81626e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1139078e170\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bav1665703126798__p_d114998e1_d114999e1_d115000e1\">When the field definition is copied to the layout, the XHTML source code similar to the following:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;x-subst name=\"TEXT_AREA.MY_ENTITY.MY_MODEL\" type=\"textarea\"&gt;\n &lt;textarea name=\"TEXT_AREA.MY_ENTITY.MY_MODEL\"&gt;&lt;/textarea&gt;\n&lt;/x-subst&gt;\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qgh1719468563350.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Text</a><p>Represents a text field and can be used to display and enter data.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7421360\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7421360\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "TextArea Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 13, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 TextArea The TextArea widget represents a text field in a static server page and can be used to display and enter data on multiple lines. XHTML Specification: <x-subst type=\"textarea\"> For more information, see <x-subst type=\"WidgetType\"> . Widget Properties Table 1. Widget Properties Property Description/More Information Exclude Exclude the field if it does not need to be sent to the browser. Rows Height of the field. Columns Width of the field. Description When the field definition is copied to the layout, the XHTML source code similar to the following: <x-subst name=\"TEXT_AREA.MY_ENTITY.MY_MODEL\" type=\"textarea\"> <textarea name=\"TEXT_AREA.MY_ENTITY.MY_MODEL\"></textarea> </x-subst> Copy Related Links Text Represents a text field and can be used to display and enter data. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}